snippet.title: Hazardous Tactics | Hazard Hero Trailer | Overwatch 2
snippet.description:
If you’re in it with him, you’re in it for life.

See what kind of chaos he and the Phreaks are causing on Oasis in our newest Hero Trailer, ‘Hazardous Tactics’.

And play as our newest Tank Hero for a limited time Nov 22-25 before Hazard officially arrives in Season 14.

Overwatch 2 is free to play for everyone on console & PC!
_
